---
description: Prefer inline confirmation UI over browser alert/confirm dialogs
alwaysApply: true
---

# No browser confirmation dialogs

Never use `window.alert`, `window.confirm`, or `window.prompt` for user confirmations.

Use an in-page confirmation pattern instead (e.g. replace a destructive action button with "Go back" and "Confirm", or an in-app modal that matches the existing UI).
